metadata.name: I Remember TheFuture, But I Have Forgotten ThePast
metadata.description:
- no time, no place
- memories but fractionalized, framed and distorted.
- a melancholic acid trip.
- a lone eyeball, a doorway, an entrance to the night sky.
- a goddess but not as we remember her.
- pete.
- nostalgia, of course, but trapped in a window...
